org.hibernate.sql.results.spi

Interface FetchParentAccess

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    CompositeInitializer, EntityInitializer

    public interface FetchParentAccess
    Serves as a link to a fetch's parent providing access to the parent instance in relation to the current "row" being processed.
